edit_issue 66 "[FEATURE] S3-03 Backend: Sync bidireccional Quotes + conflictos (Empresa/PRO)" $'## Description\nPull/push de presupuestos y conflictos de edición concurrente.\n\n## Problem It Solves\nEvita “pisados” y permite operar con programa contable externo.\n\n## Proposed Solution\n- [ ] Pull quotes remoto + upsert local\n- [ ] Push quotes local vía outbox\n- [ ] Si ambos cambiaron -> SyncConflict open\n- [ ] Endpoints:\n  - [ ] listar conflictos\n  - [ ] resolver (usar local / usar remoto)\n\n### Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Conflictos no pisan datos y requieren resolución\n\n## Alternative Solutions\n“Last write wins” -> peligroso.\n\n## Mockups or Examples\nN/A\n\n## Additional Context\nDepends on #65 y #61.'

